{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1290,"text":"I want you to touch your face."},{"time":3586,"text":"Go on."},{"time":5586,"text":"What do you feel?"},{"time":7013,"text":"Soft? Squishy?"},{"time":9493,"text":"It's you, right? You're feeling you?"},{"time":13109,"text":"Well, it's not quite true."},{"time":15387,"text":"You're actually feeling\nthousands of microscopic creatures"},{"time":18656,"text":"that live on our face and fingers."},{"time":22481,"text":"You're feeling some of the fungi"},{"time":24227,"text":"that drifted down\nfrom the air ducts today."},{"time":27131,"text":"They set off our allergies"},{"time":29122,"text":"and smell of mildew."},{"time":32045,"text":"You're feeling some\nof the 100 billion bacterial cells"},{"time":36213,"text":"that live on our skin."},{"time":38453,"text":"They've been munching away\nat your skin oils and replicating,"},{"time":42383,"text":"producing the smells of body odor."},{"time":45564,"text":"You're likely even touching\nthe fecal bacteria"},{"time":48503,"text":"that sprayed onto you the last time\nyou flushed a toilet,"},{"time":52187,"text":"or those bacteria that live\nin our water pipes"},{"time":55335,"text":"and sprayed onto you\nwith your last shower."},{"time":58666,"text":"Sorry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59841,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":61333,"text":"You're probably even giving\na microscopic high five"},{"time":64921,"text":"to the two species of mites\nthat live on our faces,"},{"time":68670,"text":"on all of our faces."},{"time":70877,"text":"They've spent the night\nsquirming across your face"},{"time":73547,"text":"and having sex on the bridge of your nose."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76419,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":79970,"text":"Many of them are now leaking\ntheir gut contents onto your pores."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84156,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86236,"text":"Now look at your finger."},{"time":88366,"text":"How's it feel? Gross?"},{"time":90491,"text":"In desperate need of soap or bleach?"},{"time":94372,"text":"That's how you feel now,"},{"time":96010,"text":"but it's not going to be\nhow you feel in the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99454,"text":"For the last 100 years,"},{"time":101403,"text":"we've had an adversarial relationship"},{"time":103404,"text":"with the microscopic life nearest us."},{"time":106043,"text":"If I told you there was\na bug in your house"},{"time":108189,"text":"or bacteria in your sink,"},{"time":109447,"text":"there was a human-devised\nsolution for that,"},{"time":111798,"text":"a product to eradicate, exterminate,"},{"time":114958,"text":"disinfect."},{"time":116843,"text":"We strive to remove most\nof the microscopic life in our world now."},{"time":121822,"text":"But in doing so, we're ignoring\nthe best source of new technology"},{"time":126539,"text":"on this planet."},{"time":128624,"text":"The last 100 years have featured\nhuman solutions to microbial problems,"},{"time":134294,"text":"but the next 100 years will feature\nmicrobial solutions to human problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140511,"text":"I'm a scientist, and I work\nwith researchers"},{"time":142904,"text":"at North Carolina State University\nand the University of Colorado"},{"time":146204,"text":"to uncover the microscopic\nlife that is nearest us,"},{"time":150817,"text":"and that's often in our most intimate\nand boring environments,"},{"time":154709,"text":"be it under our couches, in our backyards,"},{"time":157891,"text":"or in our belly buttons."},{"time":160083,"text":"I do this work because it turns out\nthat we know very little"},{"time":162977,"text":"about the microscopic life\nthat's nearest us."},{"time":166281,"text":"As of a few years ago,\nno scientist could tell you"},{"time":168778,"text":"what bugs or microorganisms\nlive in your home --"},{"time":172508,"text":"your home, the place you know\nbetter than anywhere else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176607,"text":"And so I and teams of others"},{"time":178371,"text":"are armed with Q-tips and tweezers"},{"time":180588,"text":"and advanced DNA techniques"},{"time":182478,"text":"to uncover the microscopic\nlife nearest us."},{"time":186222,"text":"In doing so, we found\nover 600 species of bugs"},{"time":190306,"text":"that live in USA homes,"},{"time":192230,"text":"everything from spiders and cockroaches"},{"time":194751,"text":"to tiny mites that cling to feathers."},{"time":198090,"text":"And we found over 100,000 species\nof bacteria and fungi"},{"time":203439,"text":"that live in our dust bunnies,"},{"time":205478,"text":"thousands more that live\non our clothes or in our showers."},{"time":210326,"text":"We've gone further still,"},{"time":211894,"text":"and we looked at the microorganisms"},{"time":213634,"text":"that live inside the bodies\nof each of those bugs in our home."},{"time":218508,"text":"In each bug, for example, a wasp,"},{"time":221942,"text":"we see a microscopic jungle\nunfold in a petri plate,"},{"time":226176,"text":"a world of hundreds of vibrant species."},{"time":229477,"text":"Behold the biological cosmos!"},{"time":233531,"text":"So many of the species\nyou're looking at right now"},{"time":235984,"text":"don't yet have names."},{"time":237903,"text":"Most of the life around us\nremains unknown."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241830,"text":"I remember the first time I discovered\nand got to name a new species."},{"time":245357,"text":"It was a fungus that lives\nin the nest of a paper wasp."},{"time":248875,"text":"It's white and fluffy,"},{"time":251124,"text":"and I named it \"mucor nidicola,\""},{"time":253692,"text":"meaning in Latin that it lives\nin the nest of another."},{"time":257952,"text":"This is a picture of it\ngrowing on a dinosaur,"},{"time":260820,"text":"because everyone\nthinks dinosaurs are cool."},{"time":264686,"text":"At the time, I was in graduate school,"},{"time":267026,"text":"and I was so excited\nthat I had found this new life form."},{"time":270772,"text":"I called up my dad, and I go,"},{"time":272572,"text":"\"Dad! I just discovered\na new microorganism species.\""},{"time":276574,"text":"And he laughed and he goes,"},{"time":278099,"text":"\"That's great. I hope you also\ndiscovered a cure for it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":281391,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":282861,"text":"\"Cure it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":285202,"text":"Now, my dad is my biggest fan,"},{"time":287933,"text":"so in that crushing moment where he wanted\nto kill my new little life form,"},{"time":292327,"text":"I realized that actually I had failed him,"},{"time":294897,"text":"both as a daughter and a scientist."},{"time":297082,"text":"In my years toiling away in labs\nand in people's backyards,"},{"time":301032,"text":"investigating and cataloging\nthe microscopic life around us,"},{"time":304736,"text":"I'd never made clear\nmy true mission to him."},{"time":308444,"text":"My goal is not to find technology"},{"time":310384,"text":"to kill the new microscopic\nlife around us."},{"time":313315,"text":"My goal is to find new technology\nfrom this life, that will help save us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319495,"text":"The diversity of life in our homes is more\nthan a list of 100,000 new species."},{"time":325271,"text":"It is 100,000 new sources\nof solutions to human problems."},{"time":330448,"text":"I know it's hard to believe\nthat anything that's so small"},{"time":333173,"text":"or only has one cell"},{"time":334355,"text":"can do anything powerful,"},{"time":335698,"text":"but they can."},{"time":337059,"text":"These creatures\nare microscopic alchemists,"},{"time":339928,"text":"with the ability to transform\ntheir environment"},{"time":342810,"text":"with an arsenal of chemical tools."},{"time":345925,"text":"This means that they can live\nanywhere on this planet,"},{"time":348932,"text":"and they can eat whatever\nfood is around them."},{"time":352552,"text":"This means they can eat everything\nfrom toxic waste to plastic,"},{"time":358075,"text":"and they can produce waste products\nlike oil and battery power"},{"time":362614,"text":"and even tiny nuggets of real gold."},{"time":366729,"text":"They can transform the inedible\ninto nutritive."},{"time":370747,"text":"They can make sugar into alcohol."},{"time":373926,"text":"They give chocolate its flavor,"},{"time":375863,"text":"and soil the power to grow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378453,"text":"I'm here to tell you"},{"time":379644,"text":"that the next 100 years will feature\nthese microscopic creatures"},{"time":382815,"text":"solving more of our problems."},{"time":384960,"text":"And we have a lot of problems\nto choose from."},{"time":387762,"text":"We've got the mundane:\nbad-smelling clothes or bland food."},{"time":392464,"text":"And we've got the monumental:"},{"time":394525,"text":"disease, pollution, war."},{"time":399326,"text":"And so this is my mission:"},{"time":401034,"text":"to not just catalog\nthe microscopic life around us,"},{"time":404288,"text":"but to find out what it's uniquely\nwell-suited to help us with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408681,"text":"Here's an example."},{"time":410070,"text":"We started with a pest,"},{"time":411726,"text":"a wasp that lives on many of our homes."},{"time":414707,"text":"Inside that wasp, we plucked out\na little-known microorganism species"},{"time":419658,"text":"with a unique ability:"},{"time":421775,"text":"it could make beer."},{"time":423886,"text":"This is a trait that only\na few species on this planet have."},{"time":427435,"text":"In fact, all commercially produced\nbeer you've ever had"},{"time":430320,"text":"likely came from one of only\nthree microorganism species."},{"time":434729,"text":"Yet our species, it could make\na beer that tasted like honey,"},{"time":439596,"text":"and it could also make\na delightfully tart beer."},{"time":443043,"text":"In fact, this microorganism species\nthat lives in the belly of a wasp,"},{"time":447607,"text":"it could make a valuable sour beer"},{"time":449928,"text":"better than any other species\non this planet."},{"time":454676,"text":"There are now four species\nthat produce commercial beer."},{"time":459197,"text":"Where you used to see a pest,"},{"time":461536,"text":"now think of tasting\nyour future favorite beer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465925,"text":"As a second example,"},{"time":467478,"text":"I worked with researchers\nto dig in the dirt in people's backyards."},{"time":471493,"text":"There, we uncovered a microorganism\nthat could make novel antibiotics,"},{"time":475574,"text":"antibiotics that can kill\nthe world's worst superbugs."},{"time":479690,"text":"This was an awesome thing to find,"},{"time":482923,"text":"but here's the secret:"},{"time":485164,"text":"for the last 60 years,"},{"time":487108,"text":"most of the antibiotics on the market"},{"time":489421,"text":"have come from similar soil bacteria."},{"time":492269,"text":"Every day, you and I\nand everyone in this room"},{"time":495318,"text":"and on this planet,"},{"time":497084,"text":"are saved by similar soil bacteria\nthat produce most of our antibiotics."},{"time":503225,"text":"Where you used to see dirt,"},{"time":504922,"text":"now think of medication."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508402,"text":"Perhaps my favorite example\ncomes from colleagues"},{"time":511072,"text":"who are studying\na pond scum microorganism,"},{"time":513992,"text":"which is tragically named after\nthe cow dung it was first found in."},{"time":518388,"text":"It's pretty unremarkable\nand would be unworthy of discussion,"},{"time":522370,"text":"except that the researchers found\nthat if you feed it to mice,"},{"time":525916,"text":"it vaccinates against PTSD."},{"time":529842,"text":"It vaccinates against fear."},{"time":533418,"text":"Where you used to see pond scum,\nnow think of hope."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538077,"text":"There are so many more microbial examples"},{"time":540505,"text":"that I don't have time\nto talk about today."},{"time":543122,"text":"I gave you examples of solutions\nthat came from just three species,"},{"time":548530,"text":"but imagine what those other\n100,000 species in your dust bunnies"},{"time":552900,"text":"might be able to do."},{"time":554751,"text":"In the future, they might be able\nto make you sexier"},{"time":558758,"text":"or smarter"},{"time":561035,"text":"or perhaps live longer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":564483,"text":"So I want you to look\nat your finger again."},{"time":567185,"text":"Think about all those\nmicroscopic creatures"},{"time":569495,"text":"that are unknown."},{"time":570966,"text":"Think about in the future\nwhat they might be able to do"},{"time":573995,"text":"or make"},{"time":575708,"text":"or whose life they might be able to save."},{"time":579071,"text":"How does your finger feel right now?"},{"time":581502,"text":"A little bit powerful?"},{"time":584564,"text":"That's because you're feeling the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":587210,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588803,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}